    Installing a Model Variable Naming System

    Brackett (1977)

    brackett_1977.Rd

    Stem Volume Models

    vsa = 10^a * dsob^b * hst^c

    • vsa [ft^3] - volume of the entire stem, including top and stump

    • dsob [in] - diameter of the stem, outside bark at breast height

    • hst [ft] - total height of the stem
